'''Middle-earth Calendar 2006''' was published by mlda fronta, Praha, Czech Republic. The calendar features watercolor or gouache illustrations by [[Martin Zhouf]].

* ISBN 80-204-0984-X
* Dimensions: 11 3/8 x 11 3/8 inches
* Punched hanging hole
* Shrink-wrapped
